OE PROGRAM 10

Amazon Macie Cloud Security Service

Aim
To detect sensitive data using Amazon Macie.

Step 1 Open Macie

1. Search Macie.
2. Open Amazon Macie.

Step 2 Enable Macie

1. Click Get Started.
2. Enable Macie.

Step 3 Select S3 Buckets

1. Open S3 bucket inventory.
2. Select required bucket.

Step 4 Run Sensitive Data Discovery

1. Create classification job.
2. Start scan.
3. Wait for analysis.

Step 5 View Findings

1. Open Findings section.
2. Observe alerts and reports.

Result
Amazon Macie security scan completed successfully.
